                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Ryan</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1890-07-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 27, 1890</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Ryan is instructed, with the aid of Mr. Mizner, to make inquiries as to the
                    cause and the responsibility of the stopping of communication between Washington
                    and Central America.</p>
            </div>
